.TH MD-ADD-COPYRIGHT 1 "February 2026" "md-add-copyright" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
md-add-copyright \- normalize and append markdown copyright footer blocks
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B md-add-copyright
[\fIOPTIONS\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B md-add-copyright
scans markdown files, normalizes copyright footer blocks, and appends a standard footer block when needed.

If existing copyright text differs from the computed target text, the script prompts for
confirmation before updating unless
.B --update
is supplied.

Duplicate and broken footer blocks are detected, reported, and consolidated into one
canonical footer block.

With no arguments, it scans all
.B *.md
files in and below the current directory and prompts before continuing.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \--check
Report files that would change without modifying them.
.TP
.B \--verbose
Print files that were modified in normal mode.
.TP
.B \--quiet
Suppress non-error output.
.TP
.B \--json
Emit machine-readable summary output.
.TP
.B \--detect-year
Detect year from repository first commit year, else file mtime year.
.TP
.B \--update
Force overwrite existing/differing footer blocks without interactive confirmation.
.TP
.B \--year \fIYYYY\fR
Manually set copyright year (overrides
.BR \--detect-year ).
.TP
.B \--owner \fINAME\fR
Manually set copyright owner name.
.TP
.B \--path \fIDIR\fR
Restrict processing to a target directory.
.TP
.B \--file \fIFILE\fR
Restrict processing to a single markdown file.
.TP
.B \-h, \--help
Show help and exit.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Success; no check-mode violations.
.TP
.B 1
Check mode found files needing changes.
.TP
.B 2
Invalid arguments or target path/file issues.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
Scan current directory tree (with prompt):
.B md-add-copyright
.TP
Dry-run check mode:
.B md-add-copyright --check
.TP
Process one file verbosely:
.B md-add-copyright --file docs/readme.md --verbose
.TP
Use detected year for a directory:
.B md-add-copyright --detect-year --path docs
.TP
Set explicit year and owner:
.B md-add-copyright --year 2024 --owner "Acme Corp" --path docs
.TP
Non-interactive overwrite (CI-safe):
.B md-add-copyright --path docs --owner "Acme Corp" --detect-year --update
.SH AUTHOR
Alex Atkinson and contributors.
